snippet.title: Midnight Mayhem - Announcement Teaser
snippet.description:
Midnight Mayhem on Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/2890060/Midnight_Mayhem

A team of humans vs an invisible monster with ever evolving abilities. Co-op pvp horror game best played with friends! 

Join the Discord: https://discord.gg/DGGtACxwrX


Thank you very much to Frozd and Fruxz on Discord for helping me record this trailer!
